snippet.title: The Family Man S3 - Official Trailer | Raj & DK | Manoj Bajpayee, Jaideep Ahlawat | Prime Video IN
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
The Family Man Season 3 Official Trailer 

SERIES:
"The Family Man," created by Raj & DK, an edgy and thrilling series on Prime Video, follows the life of Srikant Tiwari, a seemingly ordinary middle-class man who secretly works for the Threat Assessment and Surveillance Cell( TASC), a fictional cell of the National Investigation Agency in Mumbai. Balancing the demands of his high-stakes job and his family, life proves increasingly challenging as Srikant navigates dangerous missions against terrorists while trying to be a present husband and father. As he dives deeper into the murky world of espionage, Srikant must protect his loved ones from the perils of his covert profession, all while grappling with moral dilemmas that test his integrity and loyalty.

SEASON:
Outlawed and on the run, Srikant Tiwari faces sinister forces threatening to ignite chaos in Northeast India, uncovering a conspiracy that could plunge the nation into war.

Created by: Raj & DK

Directed by: Raj & DK, Suman Kumar, Tusshar Seyth
Produced by: Raj & DK
Written by Suman Kumar, Raj & DK
Screenplays by: Suman Kumar, Raj & DK, Sudhish Kamath, Nikhil Gonsalves  
Dialogues: Sumit Arora

Associate Producer: Anuradha Sharma
Executive Producer: Vikesh Bhutani, Ankita Batra
Associate Director: Chesta Goswami

Director Of Photography: Jay Charola
Production Designer: Parichit Paralkar
Editor: Sumeet Kotian
Post-Production Producer: Jespal Nadar
Action Directors: Yannick Ben Haddou, Aejaz Gulab

Background Score: Ketan Sodha

Casting Director: Mukesh Chhabra CSA 

First Assistant Director: Durgesh Pratap Singh 
Additional Writing: Suhas Navarathna
Production Supervisor: Utkarsha Kohli 
Special Advisor: Bimal Parekh

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages â€“ including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal â€“ The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Videoâ€™s video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures â€“ Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. snippet.title: Man Vs Baby | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
After a job looking after a high-tech mansion ended in disaster thanks to an irritating insect in Man vs Bee, Trevor Bingley (Rowan Atkinson) has left the stressful world of housesitting for the quieter life of a school caretaker. That is, until a lucrative offer to look after a luxury London penthouse over Christmas proves too tempting to resist. But on the last day of term, when no one comes to collect the Baby Jesus from the school nativity, Trevor finds himself with another undersized and very unexpected companion. With a penthouse to protect and a baby to burp, will Trevor be able to have the calm Christmas he hopes for, or will festivities descend into chaos?

snippet.title: The Man of Masses #NTR garu will launch the wild and powerful #MowgliTeaser tomorrow at 4:05 PM â¤â€ðŸ”¥
snippet.description:
Mowgli is an upcoming unique romantic action drama set deep within a forest backdrop. Directed by National Award-winning filmmaker Sandeep Raj (Colour Photo), Produced by TG Vishwa Prasad and Krithi Prasad under People Media Factory Banner.The film has cinematography by Rama Maruthi M, while Kaala Bhairava scores the music. The work is co-written by Rama Maruthi M and Radhakrishna Reddy The technical team also includes Peekay as editor, Kiran Mamidi as art director, and Natraj Madigonda choreographing the action sequences.

Mowgli 2025 will arrive in cinemas on December 12th, 2025.

Cast: Roshan Kanakala, Sakkshi Mhadolkar

snippet.title: Michael | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
MICHAEL - in cinemas soon.
____ 
Michael is the cinematic portrayal of the life and legacy of one of the most influential artists the world has ever known.
 
The film tells the story of Michael Jacksonâ€™s life beyond the music, tracing his journey from the discovery of his extraordinary talent as the lead of the Jackson Five, to the visionary artist whose creative ambition fueled a relentless pursuit to become the biggest entertainer in the world.
 
Highlighting both his life off-stage and some of the most iconic performances from his early solo career, the film gives audiences a front-row seat to Michael Jackson as never before. This is where his story begins.
 
Michael stars Jaafar Jackson in his feature film debut, Nia Long (Empire, The Best Man franchise), Laura Harrier (BlacKkKlansman, Spider-Man: Homecoming) and Juliano Krue Valdi (The Loud House, Arco), with Miles Teller (Top Gun: Maverick, Whiplash) and two-time Academy AwardÂ® nominee Colman Domingo (Sing Sing, Rustin).
 
Directed by Antoine Fuqua, the award-winning filmmaker of Training Day, Olympus Has Fallen and The Equalizer franchise, from a screenplay by three-time Academy AwardÂ® nominee John Logan (Gladiator, The Aviator), the film is produced by Academy AwardÂ® winner Graham King (The Departed, Bohemian Rhapsody), John Branca (executive producer This Is It, Thriller 40) and John McClain (executive producer This Is It, Michael Jackson Live at Wembley July 16, 1988).

snippet.title: O Meri Mehbooba Mehbooba Mehbooba (Music Video) - Mohammed Rafi | Dharmendra Hits Songs
snippet.description:
Enjoy the evergreen romantic track â€œO Meri Mehbooba Mehbooba Mehboobaâ€ sung by the legendary Mohammed Rafifrom the movie Dharam Veer (1977). Featuring the dynamic Dharmendra and the stunning Zeenat Aman, this melodious song . 

#OMeriMehbooba #MohammedRafi #Dharmendra #ZeenatAman #DharamVeer #LaxmikantPyarelal #BollywoodClassics #EvergreenSongs #OldBollywoodSongs #HindiSongs #BollywoodHits #RomanticSongs 

Credits: 
Singer: Mohammed Rafi
Music: Laxmikant-Pyarelal
Lyrics: Anand Bakshi
Movie: Dharam Veer
Starring: Dharmendra, Zeenat Aman
Director: Manmohan Desai
Producer: Subhash Desai
Label: Universal Music India

Lyrics: 
  
O meri mehbooba mehbooba mehbooba 

tujhey jaana hai toh jaa teri marji mera kya 

par dekh jo tu ruth kar chali jayegi 

tere saath hi mere marne ki khabar aayegi 

O meri mehbooba 

Teri chahat mera chain churaigi 

lekin tujko bhi to nind na ayegi 

main toh mar jaunga leka naam tera 

naam magar kar jaunga badnam tera 

tohba tohba phir kya hoga 

ke yaad mein meri tujko tadapaigi 

tere jaatey hi tere aane ki khabar aayegi 

O meri mehbooba 

Jo bhi meri is prem kahani ka 

par kya hoga teri mast jawani ka 

ashiq hoon main tere dil me raheta hoon 

apni nahin main tere dil ki kaheta hoon 

tohba tohba phir kya hoga 

ke yaad me teri tu pachtaegi 

yeh ruth jawani ki judai main hi guzar jayegi 

O meri mehbooba

Enjoy the evergreen romantic track â€œO Meri Mehbooba Mehbooba Mehboobaâ€ sung by the legendary Mohammed Rafifrom the movie Dharam Veer (1977). Featuring the dynamic Dharmendra and the stunning Zeenat Aman, this melodious song . 

#OMeriMehbooba #MohammedRafi #Dharmendra #ZeenatAman #DharamVeer #LaxmikantPyarelal #BollywoodClassics #EvergreenSongs #OldBollywoodSongs #HindiSongs #BollywoodHits #RomanticSongs 

Credits: 
Singer: Mohammed Rafi
Music: Laxmikant-Pyarelal
Lyrics: Anand Bakshi
Movie: Dharam Veer
Starring: Dharmendra, Zeenat Aman
Director: Manmohan Desai
Producer: Subhash Desai
Label: Universal Music India

Lyrics: 
  
O meri mehbooba mehbooba mehbooba 

tujhey jaana hai toh jaa teri marji mera kya 

par dekh jo tu ruth kar chali jayegi 

tere saath hi mere marne ki khabar aayegi 

O meri mehbooba 

Teri chahat mera chain churaigi 

lekin tujko bhi to nind na ayegi 

main toh mar jaunga leka naam tera 

naam magar kar jaunga badnam tera 

tohba tohba phir kya hoga 

ke yaad mein meri tujko tadapaigi 

tere jaatey hi tere aane ki khabar aayegi 

O meri mehbooba 

Jo bhi meri is prem kahani ka 

par kya hoga teri mast jawani ka 

ashiq hoon main tere dil me raheta hoon 

apni nahin main tere dil ki kaheta hoon 

tohba tohba phir kya hoga 

ke yaad me teri tu pachtaegi 

yeh ruth jawani ki judai main hi guzar jayegi 

O meri mehbooba

snippet.title: Matter (Official Music Video) - Sumit Parta & Panther | New Haryanvi Song 2025
snippet.description:
Presenting new Haryanvi hip hop 2025 â€“ Matter by Sumit Parta & Panther

Bringing you the raw and fearless vibe of Haryana with "Matter", the latest fire track by Sumit Parta & Panther.
This song defines real street energy â€” filled with power, attitude, and pride. With intense lyrics, bold delivery, and unstoppable flow, Matter is all about dominance, loyalty, and living with no compromise.

If you believe in your hustle and never back down â€” this oneâ€™s for you. 

Song Credits: 
Song Title: Matter
Singer: Sumit Parta & Panther
Music: Xtacy
Lyricist/Composer: Sumit Parta & Panther

Director: Mohan BeTaab
DOP: Nishan Singh

Distribution By: EYP Consulting
Distribution & Marketing Partner: EYP Creations & Warner Music India
Digitally Managed By: Prince Pannu

Lyrics:
Gaadi Uchi Uchi Rakhe Chale Talke Sedan 
Baat Lambi Koni Khiche Khde Pair Samadhan 
Sath Khaadi Panchgami Kon Gunda Paake Shayami 
Mkha Itni Re Bdi Koni Kise Ki Dukan 

Yaari Dosti Me Sara Ghar Phuk Dewa 
Par Yaari Dosti Me Koni Roli Chalya Kre 
Jiki Nasa Me Se Pani Woye Kre Samjhota 
 Mhare Matter  Me Sun Sidhi Goli Chalya  Kre 

Bair Mhare Chori Sun Dada Layi Chalre H
Gelya Chacha Tau Aale Mere Bhai Chalre H 
Kayi Sale Mere Laan Ki Sakeem Sochre H 
Anty Party Te  Krn Collab Pochre H 

Phle Karam Kand Krya Ib Bnya Hu Me  Singer 
Choro Jaata Ko  Sage Bishnoiya Ka Tinger 
Adhe Shise Khule Bhar Kade Rakhe Chora Finger
5,7 Bhai Paad Dewa Karwayi 
Konya Krke Yo Chora Kathi Toli Chalya Krya 
Jiki Nasa Me Se Pani Woye Kre Samjhota 
Mhare Matter  Me Sun Sidhi Goli Chalya Kre 

Ye Ghoda Chalta Bhi Aur Jalta Bhi
Bas Bhaagta Bhagataa Lekin Peecha Hat-ta Nahi
Ye Ghoda Jeet Dilata Aur Karta Barbaadi
Deta Nahi Maafi Hai Karta Sardari
Aur Faadein Beech Se Gar Bane Koi Jyada Patwari

Raub Jamata Ye Gaddafi Nahi Jhukta Bhale Hi Katta Sir
Mujhe Gaddari Dikhe Minute Se Pehle Got The Vision Of Gandhari
Hoti Mahabharat Tune Buri Nazar Se Dekh Li Gar Meri Panchali
Tere Chacha Bappa Sabki Karwadu Baikunth Tayyari
Aur Sun
Kam Se Jyaada Hai Zubaan Ki Izzat
Aukat Se Jyaada Karte Iman Ki Izzat
Chadhai Se Jyaada Ache Insan Ki
Hum Bhaukal Se Zyaada Karte Ache Khandan Ki Izzat
Gunday Badmash Company Me Jaise Ye Yashraj Ki Picture
Pakke Usool, Lathi Hai Har Sanp Ki Ksimat
Naseeb Me Bheji Bhagwan Ne Pehli Ashiqui Likh Kar
Aur Duji Maut Seene Pe Goli Hath Me Pistol

Hoti Pitayi Lage Kohli Mara Kare
Judge Sab Bole Galat Karam Pe Tere Moti Dhara Lage
Khatey Bikaneri Na Goli Guli Khaya Kare
Panther Bhaiya Jaha Phonchey Og Og Nara Lage

Mkha Kaan Khol Dhyan Te Tu Baat Sun Chooti 
Badmasha Ki Re Koi Prem Khani Konya Hoti 
Tane Mare Subha Shyam Fer  Bole Ga Re Gaam 
Gundya Gelya Link H Flane Ki H Poti 
Karke Ne Kand Kde Bhaje Koni Yaar 
Mhari Sadka Pe Gadi Ye Slowly Chalya Kre 

Jiki Nasa Me Se Pani Woye Kre Samjhota 
Mhare Matter  Me Sun Sidhi Goli Chalya Kre



Stay Tuned & Subscribe/Follow me on:
* Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/c/SumitParta
* Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/sumitparta09/

snippet.title: NZ vs WI | 3rd T20I | Highlights | West Indies Tour Of New Zealand 2025
snippet.description:
New Zealand won the third T20I against the West Indies by 9 runs in a match played on November 9, 2025, at Saxton Oval in Nelson. The victory gives New Zealand a 2-1 lead in the five-match series. New Zealand batted first and posted a total of 177 for 9. West Indies made a strong late comeback but fell short of the target in the final over, scoring 168 runs.

localized.title: NZ vs WI | 3rd T20I | Highlights | West Indies Tour Of New Zealand 2025
localized.description:
New Zealand won the third T20I against the West Indies by 9 runs in a match played on November 9, 2025, at Saxton Oval in Nelson. The victory gives New Zealand a 2-1 lead in the five-match series. New Zealand batted first and posted a total of 177 for 9. West Indies made a strong late comeback but fell short of the target in the final over, scoring 168 runs.
